642762ee37ed5.mp4?t=1655744295\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891350/extras/896fa7fec3f9deb5907ab81e8c6f5c55.avif?t=1655744295\" width=600 height=109 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>50 sticks to collect<br></li><li>Designed for crosswords lovers;<br></li><li>Solve 50 puzzles carefully created;<br></li><li>Enjoy 23 beautiful landscapes;<br></li><li>Choose the level of difficulty that you want to face (Easy, Normal or Hard);<br></li><li>Original soundtrack, specially composed to help you keep your focus and concentration;<br></li><li>Everything in the game was made with a lot of love and craftsmanship;</li></ul>",
